All of them were skilful musicians. Everyone enjoyed listening to their melodies and dancing to their rhythms!
These skillful musicians wanted to choose a leader. The greatest among them would be their king.', NULL);
Tongoli spoke first, "I am the greatest. I sing high and I sing low. I have many strings of different pitches. I can sing alone and in groups. The young and old love dancing to my music. I even lead Fumbo in songs."', NULL);
Fumbo continued, "People dance to my tunes like their backs are breaking! Whether in times of joy or in times sorrow I make people dance!  Children like imitating my songs like ''Coko ma nyoro no dwoki i dak''."', NULL);
Gwara gave a loud blast and said, "Am loud and I attract attention. However, I am not better than Bul. So I propose him as our king."', NULL);
Sos had been quiet all along. Now he spoke, "Comrades, I have always sung with the rest of you. You are all skillful musicians. However, the best choice for our king is Bul."', NULL);
Finally, the skilful musicians chose Bul as their king.
Ever since then Bul has been the king of music. That is why Bul is in every home at the foot of the faraway hills.', NULL);
